'''Estadio Jorge Leonidas García''' is a [[football (soccer)|football]] [[stadium]] in [[Trujillo, Honduras|Trujillo]], [[Honduras]].  It is currently used mostly for football matches and is the home stadium of [[Unión Ájax]].  The stadium holds 4,000 people. 

