'''Atherton Racing''', competing officially as '''Trek Factory Racing''', formerly as '''GT Factory Racing'''  ({{UCI code|ANC}}), is a professional [[mountain bike racing]] [[cycling team|team]] competing in the [[UCI Mountain Bike World Cup|World Cup]] and [[UCI Mountain Bike & Trials World Championships|World Champs]], as well as national level events, in the [[Downhill cycling|downhill]] category. The team began as '''Animal Commençal'''.

